pg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Tr\u00e1i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1edbi n\u1ed7i bu\u1ed3n c\u1ee7a Senegal</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"H\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Colombia vs Senegal b\u1ea3ng H World Cup 2018 \u1ea3nh 12\" title=\"Senegal\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/29/12.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Senegal l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n ch\u00e2u Phi cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi World Cup</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/colombia-gap-han-du-xuat-sac-gianh-ngoi-dau-bang-421-189900.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/28/colombia-gap-han-du-xuat-sac-gianh-ngoi-dau-bang.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/colombia-gap-han-du-xuat-sac-gianh-ngoi-dau-bang-421-189900.html\">Colombia g\u1eb7p h\u1ea1n d\u00f9 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc gi\u00e0nh ng\u00f4i \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng</span><br>\r\nTrong chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110T Senegal, HLV Pekerman \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadn tin d\u1eef khi ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t James Rodriguez d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/hlv-senegal-chung-toi-cung-rat-xung-dang-di-tiep-421-189899.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/29/hlv-senegal-chung-toi-cung-rat-xung-dang-di-tiep.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/hlv-senegal-chung-toi-cung-rat-xung-dang-di-tiep-421-189899.html\">HLV Senegal: &ldquo;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u0169ng r\u1ea5t x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng \u0111i ti\u1ebfp&rdquo;</span><br>\r\nHLV Aliou Cisse ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Senegal vs Colombia, nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n 42 tu\u1ed5i kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u00e2u Phi c\u0169ng r\u1ea5t x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng \u0111i ti\u1ebfp.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-colombia-vs-senegal-461-189886.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/28/20180628T163811Z_1_MTZEE6S1I3NZF_RTRFIPP_800_SOCCERWORLDCUPSENCOL.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-colombia-vs-senegal-461-189886.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Senegal 0-1 Colombia (B\u1ea3ng H World Cup 2018)</span><br>\r\nB\u00e0n th\u1eafng duy nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb c\u00fa \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u, trung v\u1ec7 Mina hi\u1ec7n kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Barca \u0111\u00e3 ghi b\u00e0n duy nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng 1/8 trong khi Senegal b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i cay \u0111\u1eafng.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"700","checkdouble":"189921"},{"date":"08:22 29/06","title":"Panama v\u00e0 Tunisia c\u00f9ng l\u1eadp k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c trong ng\u00e0y chia tay World Cup","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/29/bo-dao-nha-khong-co-su-khac-biet-chi-co-su-khac-biet-den-tu-cristiano-ronaldo-.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>C\u1ea3 Panama v\u00e0 Tunisia \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u d\u1ea5u \u1ea5n \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u0103m nay. Nh\u01b0ng \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng, c\u00e1c C\u0110V c\u1ee7a hai \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0103n m\u1eebng v\u00ec nh\u1eefng k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ea1o n\u00ean.</h2><h2>Panama gi\u00fap World Cup 2018 l\u1eadp k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Los Canaleros \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi World Cup 2018 sau hai th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp tr\u01b0\u1edbc B\u1ec9 v\u00e0 Anh \u1edf hai l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nNh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn thua n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ed3ng ngh\u0129a r\u1eb1ng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i c\u1ee7a Panama v\u1edbi Tunisia t\u1ea1i b\u1ea3ng G <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018-c421-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">World Cup 2018</span> ch\u1ec9 mang \u00fd ngh\u0129a th\u1ee7 t\u1ee5c. \u1ede b\u00ean kia chi\u1ebfn tuy\u1ebfn, Tunisia c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nB\u00e0n ph\u1ea3n l\u01b0\u1edbi nh\u00e0 c\u1ee7a Meriah \u1edf hi\u1ec7p m\u1ed9t \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a Panama v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u1edf m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i World Cup. V\u00e0 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u00f3 c\u0169ng thi\u1ebft l\u1eadp h\u00e0ng lo\u1ea1t k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c m\u1edbi cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Trung M\u0129.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng th\u1ee9 hai c\u1ee7a Panama \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u0103m nay. \u0110\u1ed3ng ngh\u0129a r\u1eb1ng <strong>t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i tham d\u1ef1 k\u1ef3 World Cup \u1edf Nga \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e3 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 2 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng</strong>. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 ch\u01b0a t\u1eebng x\u1ea3y ra \u1edf c\u00e1c v\u00f2ng chung k\u1ebft World Cup, k\u1ec3 c\u1ea3 \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u0103m 1930, th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 13 \u0111\u1ed9i tham d\u1ef1.<br />\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Tunisia ghi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng l\u1ecbch s\u1eed\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Panama vs Tunisia c\u00f9ng l\u1eadp k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c trong ng\u00e0y chia tay World Cup h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Panama vs Tunisia c\u00f9ng l\u1eadp k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c trong ng\u00e0y chia tay World Cup h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/29/bo-dao-nha-khong-co-su-khac-biet-chi-co-su-khac-biet-den-tu-cristiano-ronaldo-.png\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Ben Youssef ghi b\u00e0n th\u1ee9 2500 \u1edf s\u00e2n ch\u01a1i World Cup</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u00e0n th\u1eafng g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a c\u1ee7a Fakhreddine Ben Youssef sau gi\u1edd ngh\u1ec9 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ed9t m\u1ed1c l\u1ecbch s\u1eed t\u1ea1i World Cup. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 <strong>b\u00e0n th\u1eafng th\u1ee9 2500 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ghi</strong> t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u mang t\u1ea7m c\u1ee1 th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nC\u1ef1u tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n Marcus Allback \u0111\u00e3 ghi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng th\u1ee9 2000 \u1edf World Cup v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh n\u0103m 2006. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 12 n\u0103m, Claudio Caniggia ghi b\u00e0n cho Argentina v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi Nigeria v\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 b\u00e0n th\u1ee9 1500.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nRob Rensenbrink ghi b\u00e0n th\u1ee9 1000 \u1edf World Cup v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi Scotland n\u0103m 1978. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, Lucien Laurent l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi ghi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed World Cup cho \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi Mexico.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c sau tr\u1eadn Panama vs Tunisia:</strong><br />\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-tunisia-vs-panama-461-189902.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Panama 1-2 Tunisia (B\u1ea3ng G World Cup 2018)</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/ket-qua-tunisia-vs-panama-421-189896.html\">K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 Tunisia vs Panama tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u b\u1ea3ng G World Cup 2018</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"699","checkdouble":"189922"},{"date":"08:59 29/06","title":"D\u01b0 \u00e2m Anh 0-1 B\u1ec9: Si\u00eau ph\u1ea9m, gi\u1ea3i tr\u00ed v\u00e0 ni\u1ec1m vui chia \u0111\u1ec1u cho t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/29/du-am-anh-01-bi-sieu-pham-giai-tri-va-niem-vui-chia-deu-cho-tat-ca.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>C\u00f3 l\u1ebd hi\u1ebfm c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0o trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed, c\u1ea3 2 \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec1u\u2026 tranh nhau nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0y. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng d\u01b0 \u00e2m tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Anh vs B\u1ec9 0-1 t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng World Cup 2018.\r\n</h2><h2>M\u00e0n t\u1ea5u h\u00e0i c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh ph\u1ee9c t\u1ea1p c\u1ee7a v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp khi xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n nh\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1eed th\u1ea7n, c\u1ea3 Anh l\u1eabn B\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau gi\u00e0nh ng\u00f4i nh\u00ec b\u1ea3ng. Ch\u00ednh v\u00ec v\u1eady, HLV Gareth Southgate \u0111\u00e3 c\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ebfn 7 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t tr\u00ean b\u0103ng gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb, trong khi Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf g\u00e2y s\u1ed1c h\u01a1n v\u1edbi duy nh\u1ea5t Thibaut Courtois c\u00f2n s\u00f3t l\u1ea1i, so v\u1edbi tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">X\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u00f5 ch\u1eb3ng b\u00ean n\u00e0o mu\u1ed1n &ldquo;b\u1ecb&rdquo; th\u1eafng, B\u1ec9 l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng &ldquo;xu\u1ea5t chi\u00eau&rdquo; \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean khi c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng s\u01b0u t\u1eadp th\u1ebb v\u00e0ng. H\u1ecd v\u1eabn \u0111ang &ldquo;d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc&rdquo; Tam S\u01b0 v\u1ec1 s\u1ed1 th\u1ebb ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn, v\u00e0 th\u00eam 2 chi\u1ebfc th\u1ebb v\u00e0ng trong hi\u1ec7p 1 s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o cho \u0110T B\u1ec9 x\u1ebfp sau \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7. M\u1ed9t toan t\u00ednh h\u1ee3p l\u00fd, nh\u01b0ng khi\u1ebfn tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u1edf n\u00ean k\u00e9m h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn \u0111i r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"D\u01b0 \u00e2m tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Anh vs B\u1ec9 Si\u00eau ph\u1ea9m, gi\u1ea3i tr\u00ed v\u00e0 ni\u1ec1m vui h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"D\u01b0 \u00e2m tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Anh vs B\u1ec9 Si\u00eau ph\u1ea9m, gi\u1ea3i tr\u00ed v\u00e0 ni\u1ec1m vui h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/29/Du-am-tran-dau-Anh-vs-Bi-Sieu-pham,-giai-tri-va-niem-vui-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Adnan Januzaj gi\u00fap tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f4ng tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh g\u00e1nh xi\u1ebfc k\u1ec7ch c\u1ee1m</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u01b0ng r\u1ed3i sau khi hi\u1ec7p 1 kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i, c\u00f3 l\u1ebd Roberto Martinez \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng t\u00e0i n\u00e0o ch\u1ecbu n\u1ed5i s\u1ef1 &ldquo;l\u1ea7y l\u1ed9i&rdquo;, v\u00e0 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ea1o c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 d\u1ed3n l\u00ean t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng. Ch\u1eb3ng th\u1ebf m\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 khi b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u 6 ph\u00fat, Adnan Januzaj l\u1eadp si\u00eau ph\u1ea9m trong v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m \u0111\u1ecba h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c Jordan Pickford. C\u0169ng ph\u1ea3i n\u00f3i r\u1eb1ng, Danny Rose \u0111\u00e3 c\u1ed1 t\u00ecnh b\u1ecf qua ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 tr\u1ebb c\u1ee7a B\u1ec9 trong t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng \u0111\u00f3.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Pha l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 che m\u1edd nh\u1eefng toan t\u00ednh \u0111\u1ea7y th\u1ef1c d\u1ee5ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea3 2 \u0111\u1ed9i, v\u00e0 khi\u1ebfn c\u00e1c kh\u00e1n \u0111\u00e0i b\u00f9ng n\u1ed5. B\u1edfi suy cho c\u00f9ng, b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111em l\u1ea1i ni\u1ec1m vui cho c\u00e1c C\u0110V. C\u00f2n v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111ang thi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean s\u00e2n, c\u00f3 l\u1ebd h\u1ecd c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n suy ngh\u0129 qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ea1o c\u1ee7a HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng, v\u00e0 c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn h\u1ebft m\u00ecnh trong l\u1ea7n hi\u1ebfm hoi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u01b0a h\u1ebft, ngay sau b\u00e0n th\u1eafng n\u00e0y, kh\u00e1n gi\u1ea3 tr\u00ean to\u00e0n th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/hai-huoc-batshuayi-pha-dao-mxh-voi-man-an-mung-ngu-ngoc-nhat-world-cup-2018-421-189908.html\" target=\"_blank\">m\u00e0n \u0103n m\u1eebng ngu ng\u1ed1c nh\u1ea5t World Cup 2018 c\u1ee7a Batshuayi</span>, khi anh s\u00fat b\u00f3ng v\u00e0o c\u1ed9t v\u00e0 \u0111\u1eadp tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i tr\u00fang m\u1eb7t m\u00ecnh. \u0110\u00f3 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9, v\u00e0 Batshuayi \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"D\u01b0 \u00e2m tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Anh vs B\u1ec9 Si\u00eau ph\u1ea9m, gi\u1ea3i tr\u00ed v\u00e0 ni\u1ec1m vui cho t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"Batshuayi\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/29/hai-huoc-batshuayi-pha-dao-mxh-voi-man-an-mung-ngu-ngoc-nhat-world-cup-2018.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Batshuayi v\u00e0 pha \u0103n m\u1eebng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a n\u0103m</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Nh\u1eefng t\u00edn hi\u1ec7u t\u00edch c\u1ef1c<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u00f9 nh\u1eefng toan t\u00ednh l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 th\u1ef1c, khi <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/lam-tro-meo-de-duoc-thua-bi-southgate-noi-gi-421-189913.html\" target=\"_blank\">Gareth Southgate th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn c\u1ea5t qu\u00e2n \u0111\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho v\u00f2ng sau</span>. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, Martinez c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng b\u1eb1ng m\u1ecdi gi\u00e1 &ndash; cho th\u1ea5y h\u1ecd r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n gi\u00e0nh ng\u00f4i nh\u00ec b\u1ea3ng. Nh\u01b0ng tr\u00ean h\u1ebft, c\u1ea3 2 HLV \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u00ec chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd \u0111\u1ec1u ph\u1ea7n n\u00e0o ph\u00e1t huy t\u00e1c d\u1ee5ng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1edbn v\u00e0 thi \u0111\u1ea5u li\u00ean t\u1ee5c, nh\u1eefng v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c, suy gi\u1ea3m phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 l\u00fac n\u00e0o. B\u1edfi v\u1eady kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111i\u1ec3m r\u01a1i phong \u0111\u1ed9, m\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n B, C, D c\u0169ng tuy\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ed1i quan tr\u1ecdng. \u0110\u00f3 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng g\u00e2y b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u1edf v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp, v\u00e0 c\u1ea3 Anh l\u1eabn B\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ec1u c\u1ea7n m\u1ecdi nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 ph\u1ea3i s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1edbi Tam S\u01b0, h\u1ecd c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a Alexander-Arnold, t\u00e0i n\u0103ng tr\u1ebb c\u00f3 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean tham d\u1ef1 World Cup trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p. V\u1edbi s\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Kyle Walker v\u00e0 Kieran Trippier, sao tr\u1ebb c\u1ee7a Liverpool kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 \u01b0u ti\u00ean s\u1ed1 1, nh\u01b0ng anh \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng t\u1ed1t c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf m\u00ecnh trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y. S\u1edf h\u1eefu 9 key-pass trong kho\u1ea3ng th\u1eddi gian g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t tr\u00ean s\u00e2n, Arnold \u0111\u00e3 g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng l\u1edbn v\u1edbi Southgate.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"D\u01b0 \u00e2m tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Anh vs B\u1ec9 Si\u00eau ph\u1ea9m, gi\u1ea3i tr\u00ed v\u00e0 ni\u1ec1m vui cho t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u1ea3nh 3\" title=\"Arnold\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/29/arnold.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Arnold c\u00f3 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div><br>\r\nV\u1edbi nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i, Rashford, Vardy v\u00e0 Danny Rose \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n t\u1ed1t. Nh\u01b0ng d\u00f9 sao, \u0111i\u1ec1u quan tr\u1ecdng l\u00e0 h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u, v\u00e0 \u00edt nhi\u1ec1u c\u0169ng \u0111\u00f3ng vai tr\u00f2 quan tr\u1ecdng trong ch\u1eb7ng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ph\u00eda tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u1ee7a tuy\u1ec3n Anh.</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u00ean kia chi\u1ebfn tuy\u1ebfn, t\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean Roberto Martinez r\u1ea5t \u01b0ng \u00fd v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Adnan Januzaj &ndash; c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa Anh vs B\u1ec9. Kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng k\u1ef9 n\u0103ng \u0111\u00e3 tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n trong v\u00e0i n\u0103m v\u1eeba qua, \u0111i\u1ec1u quan tr\u1ecdng l\u00e0 Januzaj \u0111\u00e3 l\u1ea5y l\u1ea1i ph\u1ea7n n\u00e0o s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 tin c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, v\u00e0 anh s\u1ebd l\u00e0 h\u1ecdng s\u00fang sau tay \u00e1o c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf trong v\u00f2ng knock-out.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean, nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho ngh\u1ec9 c\u0169ng h\u01b0\u1edfng l\u1ee3i, khi h\u1ecd c\u00f3 th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ec3 b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0 l\u1ea5y l\u1ea1i th\u1ec3 tr\u1ea1ng t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"D\u01b0 \u00e2m tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Anh vs B\u1ec9 Si\u00eau ph\u1ea9m, gi\u1ea3i tr\u00ed v\u00e0 ni\u1ec1m vui cho t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u1ea3nh 4\" title=\"Hazard v\u00e0 Lukaku \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho ngh\u1ec9 \u1edf tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/29/5.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Hazard v\u00e0 Lukaku \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho ngh\u1ec9 \u1edf tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<h2>Chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng cho t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi B\u1ec9, r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/hlv-martinez-to-ra-hai-long-sau-khi-lo-thang-anh-421-189914.html\" target=\"_blank\">Martinez c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y bu\u1ed3n phi\u1ec1n khi &ldquo;l\u1ee1&rdquo; gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng</span>. Nh\u01b0ng d\u00f9 sao, \u0111\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i x\u1ea3y ra v\u00e0 B\u1ec9 x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn ph\u00eda tr\u01b0\u1edbc. R\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ea7n n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 th\u1ebf h\u1ec7 v\u00e0ng, ch\u1eafc h\u1eb3n Hazard v\u00e0 to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i mu\u1ed1n tranh t\u00e0i \u1edf \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p cao nh\u1ea5t v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft, \u0110T B\u1ec9 s\u1ebd ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8, khi h\u1ecd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 nh\u1ec9nh h\u01a1n. V\u00e0 n\u1ebfu v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n ch\u00e2u \u00c1, nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ebfp theo c\u1ee7a B\u1ec9 s\u1ebd c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i, v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng Mexico/Brazil \u0111ang ch\u1edd ngay sau \u0111\u00f3. N\u1ebfu \u0111i ti\u1ebfp, s\u1ebd l\u00e0 h\u00e0ng lo\u1ea1t th\u1ee9 d\u1eef nh\u01b0 Uruguay/B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha/Ph\u00e1p/Argentina \u1edf nh\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1eed th\u1ea7n.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"D\u01b0 \u00e2m tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Anh vs B\u1ec9 Si\u00eau ph\u1ea9m, gi\u1ea3i tr\u00ed v\u00e0 ni\u1ec1m vui cho t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u1ea3nh 5\" title=\"C\u1ea3 Southgate v\u00e0 Martinez \u0111\u1ec1u h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 n\u00e0y\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/29/south.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>D\u01b0 \u00e2m tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Anh vs B\u1ec9: C\u1ea3 Southgate v\u00e0 Martinez \u0111\u1ec1u h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 n\u00e0y</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00f2n v\u1edbi tuy\u1ec3n Anh, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 &ldquo;m\u1eb7t d\u00e0y&rdquo; nh\u1eadn l\u1ea5y v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 2, \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u1eb1m trong nh\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea5u d\u1ec5 th\u1edf h\u01a1n. Nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, Tam S\u01b0 c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Colombia n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n nh\u1eefng toan t\u00ednh c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd tr\u1edf n\u00ean l\u1ed1 b\u1ecbch. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ea5u r\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i, khi c\u1ea3 2 \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec1u r\u1ea5t m\u1ea1nh \u1edf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng d\u00e0n x\u1ebfp \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i nh\u1ea5t, ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 m\u01a1 v\u1ec1 v\u00f2ng b\u00e1n k\u1ebft v\u1edbi T\u00e2y Ban Nha. D\u00f9 sao, c\u00e1c C\u0110V Anh c\u0169ng r\u1ea5t n\u00f3ng l\u00f2ng ch\u1edd xem \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n tranh t\u00e0i, b\u1edfi HLV Gareth Southgate kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Colombia l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd trong v\u00f2ng 10 n\u0103m qua.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"D\u01b0 \u00e2m tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Anh vs B\u1ec9 Si\u00eau ph\u1ea9m, gi\u1ea3i tr\u00ed v\u00e0 ni\u1ec1m vui cho t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u1ea3nh 6\" title=\"X\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng chung cu\u1ed9c b\u1ea3ng G World Cup 2018\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/29/G.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>X\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng chung cu\u1ed9c b\u1ea3ng G World Cup 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"D\u01b0 \u00e2m tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Anh vs B\u1ec9 Si\u00eau ph\u1ea9m, gi\u1ea3i tr\u00ed v\u00e0 ni\u1ec1m vui cho t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u1ea3nh 7\" title=\"Anh \u0111\u00e3 n\u00e9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1eed th\u1ea7n b\u00ean tr\u00e1i\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/29/knock.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng knock-out World Cup 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/3-nguoi-chien-thang-va-3-nguoi-that-bai-sau-tran-dai-chien-vi-ngoi-nhi-bang-giua-anh-va-bi-421-189915.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/29/3-nguoi-chien-thang-va-3-nguoi-that-bai-sau-tran-dai-chien-vi-ngoi-nhi-bang-giua-anh-va-bi.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/3-nguoi-chien-thang-va-3-nguoi-that-bai-sau-tran-dai-chien-vi-ngoi-nhi-bang-giua-anh-va-bi-421-189915.html\">3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn Anh vs B\u1ec9</span><br>\r\nB\u00e0n th\u1eafng duy nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Adnan Januzaj gi\u00fap B\u1ec9 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Anh v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 1-0. C\u00f9ng \u0111i\u1ec3m qua danh s\u00e1ch 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i sau tr\u1eadn Anh vs B\u1ec9...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhung-hinh-anh-dang-nho-trong-tran-quyet-chien-vi-ngoi-nhi-giua-anh-vs-bi-421-189912.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/29/nhung-hinh-anh-dang-nho-trong-tran-quyet-chien-vi-ngoi-nhi-giua-anh-vs-bi.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhung-hinh-anh-dang-nho-trong-tran-quyet-chien-vi-ngoi-nhi-giua-anh-vs-bi-421-189912.html\">Nh\u1eefng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1edb trong &ldquo;tr\u1eadn quy\u1ebft chi\u1ebfn v\u00ec ng\u00f4i nh\u00ec&rdquo; gi\u1eefa Anh vs B\u1ec9</span><br>\r\n\u1ede l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng b\u1ea3ng G, c\u00f3 l\u1ebd c\u1ea3 2 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ec1u mu\u1ed1n nh\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Anh vs B\u1ec9 t\u1ea1i World Cup...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-bi-vs-anh-461-189901.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/29/adnan-januzaj-noi-gi-sau-ban-thang-dau-tien-cho-dt-bi.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-bi-vs-anh-461-189901.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Anh 0-1 B\u1ec9 (B\u1ea3ng G World Cup 2018)</span><br>\r\nAdnan Januzaj, th\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Old Trafford, \u0111\u00e3 ghi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng duy nh\u1ea5t kh\u00e1 \u0111\u1eb9p m\u1eaft trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111o\u1ea1t ng\u00f4i v\u1ecb s\u1ed1 1 b\u1ea3ng G World Cup 2018.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"698","checkdouble":"189924"},{"date":"08:47 29/06","title":"Mourinho \u0111\u1ed9ng vi\u00ean De Gea sau nh\u1eefng sai l\u1ea7m \u1edf World Cup 2018","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/29/khi-nhung-buoc-chan-run-ray.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Mourinho \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng \u0111\u1ed9ng vi\u00ean De Gea khi th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh n\u00e0y \u0111ang tr\u1ea3i qua m\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 World Cup th\u1ea3m h\u1ecda tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga.</h2><h2>De Gea ch\u01a1i kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u00e3 b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng 1/8 World Cup n\u0103m nay v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n thi\u1ebfu thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c. \u201cB\u00f2 t\u00f3t\u201d ch\u1ec9 th\u1eafng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 1 trong 3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng v\u00e0 th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi t\u1edbi 5 b\u00e0n thua.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nDe Gea l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1eafc nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ed7i nh\u1ea5t. Anh l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1eafc l\u1ed7i ch\u00ednh trong tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a c\u1ee7a T\u00e2y Ban Nha tr\u01b0\u1edbc B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n. V\u00e0 k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb \u0111\u00f3, De Gea c\u0169ng thi \u0111\u1ea5u thi\u1ebfu t\u1ef1 tin h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Mourinho \u0111\u1ed9ng vi\u00ean De Gea sau nh\u1eefng sai l\u1ea7m \u1edf World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Mourinho \u0111\u1ed9ng vi\u00ean De Gea sau nh\u1eefng sai l\u1ea7m \u1edf World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/29/khi-nhung-buoc-chan-run-ray.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Mourinho \u0111\u1ed9ng vi\u00ean De Gea sau nh\u1eefng sai l\u1ea7m \u1edf World Cup 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n h\u1ed3i \u0111\u1ea7u tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh HLV Hierro \u0111ang c\u00e2n nh\u1eafc \u201ctr\u1ea3m\u201d De Gea v\u00e0 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng Kepa Arrizabalaga \u1edf nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ebfp theo.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u00e2y Ban Nha s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Nga \u1edf Moscow v\u00e0o Ch\u1ee7 nh\u1eadt n\u00e0y. V\u00e0 t\u1edd Metro tin r\u1eb1ng Mourinho \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eedi cho De Gea r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u tin nh\u1eafn \u0111\u1ed9ng vi\u00ean trong su\u1ed1t th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u00e3 qua c\u1ee7a World Cup.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nD\u00f9 De Gea v\u1eabn thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ef1c xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc \u1edf Man United, ph\u1ea7n \u0111\u00f4ng C\u0110V T\u00e2y Ban Nha v\u1eabn mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ea9y c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 27 tu\u1ed5i l\u00ean gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb. Kh\u1ea3o s\u00e1t m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y c\u1ee7a t\u1edd AS cho th\u1ea5y 50% trong s\u1ed1 40.000 \u0111\u1ed9c gi\u1ea3 c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd mu\u1ed1n c\u1ef1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Atletico b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi v\u00f2ng chi\u1ebfn \u1edf tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Iran.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Mourinho b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 De Gea</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0 Mourinho \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00edch th\u00e2n l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 De Gea tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u01a1n b\u00e3o ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch ng\u00e0y m\u1ed9t m\u1ea1nh h\u01a1n trong giai \u0111o\u1ea1n g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cDe Gea l\u00e0 h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u01b0ng c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i. T\u00f4i r\u1ea5t \u0111au \u0111\u1edbn tr\u01b0\u1edbc t\u00ecnh c\u1ea3nh hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i nh\u01b0ng De Gea c\u0169ng bi\u1ebft r\u1eb1ng c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 m\u1eafc m\u1ed9t sai l\u1ea7m nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cNh\u01b0ng \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t. \u0110i\u1ec1u quan tr\u1ecdng l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc v\u1eabn s\u1ebd lu\u00f4n xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n \u1edf nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ebfp theo. V\u00e0 h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng s\u1ee3 h\u00e3i \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec c\u1ea3\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 \u0110T\u00a0T\u00e2y Ban Nha:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/tay-ban-nha-22-marocco-dau-roi-bong-dang-nha-vua-421-189595.html\">T\u00e2y Ban Nha 2-2 Morocco: \u0110\u00e2u r\u1ed3i b\u00f3ng d\u00e1ng nh\u00e0 vua</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/hlv-hierro-phat-bieu-sau-tran-tbn-22-ma-roc-421-189572.html\">HLV T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u1ea7y lo \u00e2u sau tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a nh\u1ecdc Ma R\u1ed1c</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"697","checkdouble":"189925"},{"date":"08:36 29/06","title":"Nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng tin c\u1ea7n bi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 v\u00f2ng 1/8 World Cup 2018","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/6/29/nhung-thong-tin-can-biet-ve-vong-18-world-cup-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng tin v\u1ec1 v\u00f2ng 1/8 (v\u00f2ng 16 \u0111\u1ed9i) t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Bongda24h.vn t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p v\u00e0 g\u1eedi t\u1edbi qu\u00fd \u0111\u1ed9c gi\u1ea3.</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i tham d\u1ef1<br />\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau 48 tr\u1eadn v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng, 16 \u0111\u1ed9i g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t \u1edf v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp g\u1ed3m Nga, T\u00e2y Ban Nha, B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha, Ph\u00e1p, \u0110an M\u1ea1ch, Croatia,&nbsp; Th\u1ee5y S\u0129, Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n, B\u1ec9, Anh (ch\u00e2u \u00c2u - 10/14 \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n), Uruguay, Argentina, Brazil, Colombia (Nam M\u1ef9 - 4/5), Mexico (B\u1eafc Trung M\u1ef9 - 1/3), Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n (ch\u00e2u \u00c1 - 1/5).&nbsp;<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng tin c\u1ea7n bi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 v\u00f2ng 18 World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng tin c\u1ea7n bi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 v\u00f2ng 18 World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/29/vong-18.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Trong s\u1ed1 16 \u0111\u1ed9i v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng 1/8 World Cup 2018, kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n n\u00e0o c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2u Phi.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\nKh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n n\u00e0o trong s\u1ed1 5 \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2u Phi l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng 1/8 World Cup 2018.&nbsp;<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1eddi gian<br />\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00f2ng 1/8 World Cup 2018 s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra t\u1eeb ng\u00e0y 30/6 - 4/7 (theo gi\u1edd Vi\u1ec7t Nam). C\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra theo hai khung gi\u1edd l\u00e0 21h00 v\u00e0 1h00.</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00e1c c\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ea5u<br />\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">21h00 ng\u00e0y 30/6: Ph\u00e1p vs Argentina - s\u00e2n Kazan Arena (Kazan).<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">1h00 ng\u00e0y 1/7: Uruguay vs B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha - s\u00e2n Fisht Olympic (Sochi).<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Cac cap dau tai vong 1/8 World Cup 2018.\" title=\"C\u00e1c c\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 1/8 World Cup 2018.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/29/vong-18-1.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>C\u00e1c c\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 1/8 World Cup 2018.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\n21h00 ng\u00e0y 1/7: T\u00e2y Ban Nha vs Nga - s\u00e2n Luzhniki (Moscow).<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">1h00 ng\u00e0y 2/7: Croatia vs \u0110an M\u1ea1ch - s\u00e2n Novgorod (Nizhny Novgorod).<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">21h00 ng\u00e0y 2/7: Brazil vs Mexico - s\u00e2n Cosmos Arena (Samara).<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">1h00 ng\u00e0y 3/7: B\u1ec9 vs Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n - s\u00e2n Rostov Arena (Rostov).<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">21h00 ng\u00e0y 3/7: Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n vs Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 - s\u00e2n Krestovsky (Saint Petersburg).<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">1h00 ng\u00e0y 4/7: Colombia vs Anh - s\u00e2n Otkritie Arena (Moscow).<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/vck-world-cup-2018/bang-xep-hang-41.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/29/bang-xep-hang-world-cup-2018.jpg\" alt=\"BXH World Cup 2018\" /></span><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/vck-world-cup-2018/bang-xep-hang-41.html\"> BXH VCK World Cup 2018 m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t</span><br />\r\n<span>C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt b\u1ea3ng x\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng c\u00e1c b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a VCK World Cup 2018 t\u1ea1i Nga m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t.</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\n<h2>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn v\u1ec1 v\u00f2ng 1/8 World Cup 2018:</h2>\r\n<br />\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/tran-colombia-se-la-cuoc-dau-knockout-lon-nhat-thap-ky-cua-anh-421-189909.html\">Tr\u1eadn Colombia s\u1ebd l\u00e0 cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ea5u knock-out l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t th\u1eadp k\u1ef7 c\u1ee7a Anh</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/6-diem-sang-toi-nhin-tu-that-bai-trong-tinh-toan-cua-anh-truoc-bi-421-189905.html\">6 \u0111i\u1ec3m s\u00e1ng t\u1ed1i nh\u00ecn t\u1eeb th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i trong t\u00ednh to\u00e1n c\u1ee7a Anh tr\u01b0\u1edbc B\u1ec9</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/maradona-xuat-vien-toi-dang-cang-tran-suc-song-hon-bao-gio-het-421-189895.html\">Maradona xu\u1ea5t vi\u1ec7n: &ldquo;T\u00f4i \u0111ang c\u0103ng tr\u00e0n s\u1ee9c s\u1ed1ng h\u01a1n bao gi\u1edd h\u1ebft&rdquo;</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/tin-nong-world-cup-2018/huyen-thoai-tin-tuong-thuy-dien-se-chiem-suat-di-tiep-cua-mexico-469-189760.html\">Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i tin t\u01b0\u1edfng Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n s\u1ebd gi\u00e0nh 1 su\u1ea5t \u0111i ti\u1ebfp \u1edf b\u1ea3ng F</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/hlv-argentina-nghi-sao-ve-man-vuot-cua-tu-kich-tinh-421-189694.html\">HLV Argentina ngh\u0129 sao v\u1ec1 m\u00e0n v\u01b0\u1ee3t c\u1eeda t\u1eed k\u1ecbch t\u00ednh?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/quy-tac-xep-hang-bang-dau-world-cup-2018-tai-sao-anh-vs-bi-co-the-phan-dinh-nhat-nhi-bang-the-phat-421-189499.html\">Quy t\u1eafc x\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i trong b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<strong><br type=\"_moz\" />\r\n</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>N.D (TTVN)</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"696","checkdouble":"189926"},{"date":"04:17 29/06","title":"H\u00e0i h\u01b0\u1edbc: Batshuayi ph\u00e1 \u0111\u1ea3o MXH v\u1edbi m\u00e0n \u0103n m\u1eebng ngu ng\u1ed1c nh\u1ea5t World Cup 2018","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/29/hai-huoc-batshuayi-pha-dao-mxh-voi-man-an-mung-ngu-ngoc-nhat-world-cup-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Trong tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a \u0110T B\u1ec9 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Tam S\u01b0, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Michy Batshuayi \u0103n m\u1eebng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng b\u1eb1ng m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 c\u1ed1 v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nBatshuayi l\u1ea1i &ldquo;ph\u00e1 \u0111\u1ea3o&rdquo; Internet<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c ch\u00e2n s\u00fat ch\u1ee7 l\u1ef1c Romelu Lukaku \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho ngh\u1ec9 d\u01b0\u1ee1ng s\u1ee9c trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, Michy Batshuayi \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn thay th\u1ebf. Nh\u01b0ng ch\u00e2n s\u00fat thu\u1ed9c bi\u00ean ch\u1ebf Chelsea kh\u00f4ng t\u1ea1o ra qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, ngo\u1ea1i tr\u1eeb m\u1ed9t t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng&hellip; tr\u1eddi \u01a1i \u0111\u1ea5t h\u1ee1i.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3 v\u00e0o ph\u00fat 51 c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Adnan Januzaj l\u1eadp si\u00eau ph\u1ea9m v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi \u0110T Anh, gi\u00fap B\u1ec9 v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc. Qu\u00e1 vui m\u1eebng v\u1edbi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Batshuayi \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ea1y \u0111\u1ebfn \u00f4m l\u1ea5y qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ecbnh l\u00e0m m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec \u0111\u00f3 hay ho.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"T\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng Batshuayi \u0103n m\u1eebng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng\" title=\"C\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111au ru\u1ed9t v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 c\u1ed1 Batshuayi \u0103n m\u1eebng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/29/bat.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>T\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng Batshuayi \u0103n m\u1eebng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng thay v\u00ec s\u00fat v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1ea3i t\u1ecfa, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y l\u1ea1i \u0111\u01b0a b\u00f3ng tr\u00fang c\u1ed9t d\u1ecdc m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd, sau \u0111\u00f3 b\u00f3ng&hellip; b\u1eadt ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i tr\u00fang m\u1eb7t anh. S\u1ef1 c\u1ed1 h\u00e0i h\u01b0\u1edbc n\u00e0y \u0111ang t\u1ea1o ra c\u01a1n s\u1ed1t tr\u00ean Twitter, \u0111\u1ebfn n\u1ed7i ch\u00ednh &ldquo;kh\u1ed5 ch\u1ee7&rdquo; Batshuayi c\u0169ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00ean m\u1ea1ng chia s\u1ebb c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Ahaha, t\u00f4i bi\u1ebft m\u00ecnh s\u1ebd &lsquo;\u0103n \u0111\u00f2n&rsquo; ch\u1ec9 1 ph\u00fat sau t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng n\u00e0y m\u00e0. T\u1ea1i sao t\u00f4i l\u1ea1i ngu ng\u1ed1c nh\u01b0 v\u1eady ch\u1ee9. \u0110au v\u00e3i&rdquo; &ndash; ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o 24 tu\u1ed5i b\u00e0y t\u1ecf tr\u00ean Twitter c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, c\u00f9ng h\u00e0ng lo\u1ea1t bi\u1ec3u t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u01b0\u1eddi ra n\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng n\u00e0y, \u0110T B\u1ec9 \u0111\u00e3 k\u1ebft th\u00fac v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng v\u1edbi v\u1ecb tr\u00ed d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u, v\u00e0 s\u1ebd ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n \u1edf v\u00f2ng ti\u1ebfp theo. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, \u0110T Anh \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi Colombia, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng gi\u00e0nh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 nh\u1ea5t b\u1ea3ng H.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>C\u00f9ng xem l\u1ea1i t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng Batshuayi \u0103n m\u1eebng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng<br>\r\n</strong>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/6/29/bat.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-bi-vs-anh-461-189901.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/29/clip-ban-thang-bi-vs-anh.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-bi-vs-anh-461-189901.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Anh 0-1 B\u1ec9 (B\u1ea3ng G World Cup 2018)</span><br>\r\nAdnan Januzaj, th\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Old Trafford, \u0111\u00e3 ghi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng duy nh\u1ea5t kh\u00e1 \u0111\u1eb9p m\u1eaft trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111o\u1ea1t ng\u00f4i v\u1ecb s\u1ed1 1 b\u1ea3ng G World Cup 2018.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/truc-tiep-bi-vs-anh-463-189888.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/28/ket-qua-bi-vs-anh.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/truc-tiep-bi-vs-anh-463-189888.html\">Anh 0-1 B\u1ec9 (KT): C\u1ef1u sao tr\u1ebb M.U gi\u00fap Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c Tam s\u01b0</span><br>\r\nAdnan Januzaj, th\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Old Trafford, \u0111\u00e3 ghi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng duy nh\u1ea5t kh\u00e1 \u0111\u1eb9p m\u1eaft trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111o\u1ea1t ng\u00f4i v\u1ecb s\u1ed1 1 b\u1ea3ng G World Cup 2018.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"695","checkdouble":"189908"},{"date":"06:22 29/06","title":"Tr\u1eadn Colombia s\u1ebd l\u00e0 cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ea5u knock-out l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t th\u1eadp k\u1ef7 c\u1ee7a Anh","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/29/tran-colombia-se-la-cuoc-dau-knockout-lon-nhat-thap-ky-cua-anh.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u c\u1ee7a HLV Gareth Southgate sau tr\u1eadn thua Anh 0-1 B\u1ec9 khi\u1ebfn Tam S\u01b0 m\u1ea5t ng\u00f4i \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng G v\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u Colombia \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8 World Cup 2018.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">V\u1edbi ch\u00f3ng m\u1eb7t nh\u1eefng thay \u0111\u1ed5i nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb c\u1ea3 hai, Anh thua B\u1ec9 b\u1eb1ng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng duy nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Adnan Januzaj sau c\u00fa c\u1ee9a l\u00f2ng ch\u00e2n tr\u00e1i \u0111\u1eb9p m\u1eaft c\u1ee7a c\u1ef1u th\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed3ng Man Utd. K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 n\u00e0y khi\u1ebfn Tam S\u01b0 m\u1ea5t ng\u00f4i \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng G v\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t Colombia kh\u00f3 nh\u1eb1n h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8 World Cup 2018.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Southgate ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn Anh vs B\u1ec9 thua v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 0-1 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Southgate ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn Anh vs B\u1ec9 thua v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 0-1 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/29/tran-colombia-se-la-cuoc-dau-knockout-lon-nhat-thap-ky-cua-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HLV Southgate ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn Anh vs B\u1ec9</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cTr\u1eadn Colombia s\u1ebd l\u00e0 cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ea5u knock-out l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t th\u1eadp k\u1ef7 c\u1ee7a Anh.\u201d \u2013 Kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a Gareth Southgate trong bu\u1ed5i h\u1ecdp b\u00e1o ph\u1ecfng v\u1ea5n sau tr\u1eadn <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/truc-tiep-bi-vs-anh-463-189888.html\" target=\"_blank\">Anh 0-1 B\u1ec9</span>. Th\u1eadt v\u1eady khi \u0111\u00e3 12 n\u0103m qua k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb v\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup 2006 \u1edf \u0110\u1ee9c, Tam S\u01b0 ch\u01b0a th\u1eafng th\u00eam n\u1ed5i b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 tr\u1eadn knock-out n\u00e0o \u1edf c\u00e1c gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1edbn, bao g\u1ed3m c\u1ea3 Euro.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">C\u0169ng ch\u00ednh v\u00ec m\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ed9 h\u1ec7 tr\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn \u1edf Moscow sang tu\u1ea7n, HLV 47 tu\u1ed5i m\u1edbi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 g\u1eedi l\u1eddi gi\u1ea3i th\u00edch x\u00e1c \u0111\u00e1ng cho quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh xoay tua \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ebfn n\u1ed7i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 nh\u1eadn ra c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng. Southgate n\u00f3i th\u00eam: <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cTh\u1ebf n\u00ean ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i d\u01b0\u1ee1ng s\u1ee9c cho nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 quan tr\u1ecdng. B\u1ea1n th\u1ea5y b\u00e0i h\u1ecdc t\u1eeb Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n hay ch\u00ednh Colombia, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u1ea3 Senegal n\u1ebfu h\u1ecd v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng r\u1ed3i \u0111\u1ea5y, ai c\u0169ng m\u1ea5t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ee7 ch\u1ed1t v\u00ec nh\u1eefng t\u1ea5m th\u1ebb ph\u1ea1t \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t cu\u1ed1i n\u00e0y.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cB\u1ea3n th\u00e2n t\u00f4i c\u0169ng tuy\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ed1i tin t\u01b0\u1edfng v\u00e0o m\u1ecdi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ec3 r\u1ed3i gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e2y, c\u1ea3 20 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ngo\u1ea1i tr\u1eeb hai th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf World Cup l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y. \u0110\u00f3 n\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00f4ng nh\u1eadn l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t b\u01b0\u1edbc ti\u1ebfn. T\u00f4i bi\u1ebft m\u00ecnh s\u1ebd b\u1ecb ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch, nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean kh\u00f4ng ai mong mu\u1ed1n tr\u1eadn thua n\u00e0y, nh\u01b0ng d\u00f9 sao c\u0169ng l\u00e0 b\u00e0i h\u1ecdc qu\u00fd gi\u00e1 cho ch\u00fang t\u00f4i r\u1ed3i.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">N\u1ebfu v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Colombia \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8, Anh s\u1ebd r\u1ed9ng m\u1edf con \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng th\u1eb3ng ti\u1ebfn v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean sau 28 n\u0103m khi ch\u1ec9 ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n ho\u1eb7c Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 \u1edf t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/6-diem-sang-toi-nhin-tu-that-bai-trong-tinh-toan-cua-anh-truoc-bi-421-189905.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/29/tran-colombia-se-la-cuoc-dau-knockout-lon-nhat-thap-ky-cua-anh.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/6-diem-sang-toi-nhin-tu-that-bai-trong-tinh-toan-cua-anh-truoc-bi-421-189905.html\">6 \u0111i\u1ec3m s\u00e1ng t\u1ed1i nh\u00ecn t\u1eeb th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i trong t\u00ednh to\u00e1n c\u1ee7a Anh tr\u01b0\u1edbc B\u1ec9</span><br>\r\nTr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao Premier League \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111o\u1ea1t b\u1edfi m\u1ed9t\u2026 m\u00f3n h\u00e0ng th\u1ea3i Premier League \u2013 Adnan Januzaj, c\u1ef1u th\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed3ng Man Utd. K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 Anh 0-1...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"694","checkdouble":"189909"}]}